      "date": "2019-11-02 02:15:23.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6: Verified+1\n\nPassed enforced test review-ldiskfs-dne on CentOS 7.0/x86_64 uploaded by Onyx Autotest from onyx-30vm6: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/dfd7a86d-2642-4d7b-ba41-b7e5e91beac2 ran 4 tests.",
